  <section id="mission" class="section">
    <div class="mission-layout">
      <div class="reveal">
        <div class="section-label">Our Mission</div>
        <h2 class="mission-heading">Built for <em>Players</em>. Driven by <em>Purpose.</em></h2>
        <div class="founded-tag">Founded 2015 &nbsp;&#183;&nbsp; Largest Club on Campus</div>
      </div>
      <div class="mission-text reveal">
        <p>Marquette Esports exists to <strong>unite students who are passionate about gaming</strong> &mdash; competitive or casual &mdash; and give them a home on campus to grow, compete, and thrive together.</p>
        <p>We believe esports is more than winning. It is a vehicle for <strong>teamwork, leadership, and belonging</strong>. Our club creates space where every player, regardless of skill level or background, can find their team.</p>
        <p>From organized competitive rosters to open community events, we are building a program that <strong>represents Marquette with pride</strong> &mdash; both on and off the screen.</p>
        <p>Reach us at <a href="mailto:MUEsports@marquette.edu"><strong>MUEsports@marquette.edu</strong></a></p>
      </div>
