    <div class="values-grid">
      <div class="value-card reveal"><div class="value-number">01</div><div class="value-title">Community</div><p class="value-desc">Gaming is better with others. We foster genuine friendships and a welcoming environment for every student &mdash; from first-time players to seasoned competitors. You are not just joining a club, you are joining a family.</p></div>
      <div class="value-card reveal"><div class="value-number">02</div><div class="value-title">Competition</div><p class="value-desc">We push each other to improve and represent Marquette at the highest level in the BIG East Conference. Whether you are grinding ranked or stepping into your first tournament, we will back your drive to be better.</p></div>
      <div class="value-card reveal"><div class="value-number">03</div><div class="value-title">Inclusion</div><p class="value-desc">Marquette Esports is a place for everyone. We do not care about your rank, your setup, or your background &mdash; if you love games or the gaming scene, you belong here. No gatekeeping, ever.</p></div>
      <div class="value-card reveal"><div class="value-number">04</div><div class="value-title">Marquette Spirit</div><p class="value-desc">We are Warriors on every platform &mdash; proud of our university, committed to excellence, and carrying that Golden Eagle energy into every match and every event we host.</p></div>
