  <section id="getinvolved" class="section">
    <div class="section-header reveal"><div class="section-label">Find Your Role</div><h2>Ways to Get Involved</h2><p>Whether you are here to compete, hang out, or tell the story &mdash; there is a place for you in Marquette Esports.</p></div>
    <div class="involve-grid">
      <div class="involve-card reveal">
        <div class="involve-icon">&#127942;</div>
        <div class="section-label">Competitive</div>
        <h3 class="involve-heading">Compete for Marquette</h3>
        <p class="involve-text">Try out for one of our <strong>9 competitive teams</strong> and represent Marquette in the <strong>BIG East Conference</strong> via PlayVS. We field rosters across League of Legends, Valorant, Siege, and more.</p>
        <p class="involve-text">Dues only apply if you make a competitive roster &mdash; covering your jersey and conference fees. You must be an <strong>actively enrolled Marquette student</strong> to compete.</p>
        <a href="https://pcl.gg/pages/members" target="_blank" class="involve-link">View our PlayVS page &rarr;</a>
      </div>
      <div class="involve-card reveal">
        <div class="involve-icon">&#127918;</div>
        <div class="section-label">Casual</div>
        <h3 class="involve-heading">Monthly LAN Parties</h3>
