        <p class="involve-text">We also run <strong>in-house tournaments</strong> featuring crowd favorites like <strong>Mario Kart</strong> and <strong>Super Smash Bros</strong>. Alumni are welcome to come back for LANs too!</p>
        <a href="https://club.fusionfamily.com/@/muclubsports/1651e6b5-66b0-4ccd-a123-966e2b6f03bd" target="_blank" class="involve-link">Join on Club Fusion &rarr;</a>
